WEBVTT

01:49.840 --> 01:52.800
You always said your dad passed away.

01:53.920 --> 01:55.520
I really wanted to ask

01:56.520 --> 01:59.240
how he died.

02:00.680 --> 02:01.800
He didn't die.

02:02.120 --> 02:03.780
He ran away with his mistress.

02:04.400 --> 02:07.060
My mom told my sister and me to pretend he's dead.

02:07.520 --> 02:08.960
So I swore since I was a kid

02:09.199 --> 02:10.660
that if I ever get married,

02:10.919 --> 02:13.250
I will never be as irresponsible as my dad.

02:13.320 --> 02:15.080
I will treat them well for the rest of my life,

02:15.080 --> 02:17.740
and pamper my wife and kids in the palm of my hand.

02:20.480 --> 02:23.210
You're so young, why are you thinking about this?

02:23.880 --> 02:24.680
It's not far.

02:24.920 --> 02:26.240
I've thought it through.

02:26.240 --> 02:28.320
With my grades, I'll go to a junior college at best,

02:28.320 --> 02:29.200
study for three years,

02:29.200 --> 02:31.040
and get married right after graduation.

02:31.040 --> 02:33.400
As a man, settling down and starting a career,

02:33.400 --> 02:34.530
I should definitely

02:34.760 --> 02:36.200
settle down first.

02:36.600 --> 02:38.960
My mom said after I finish my bachelor's degree,

02:38.960 --> 02:40.079
she wants me to go to grad school.

02:40.079 --> 02:41.760
Otherwise, it'll be hard to find a job.

02:41.760 --> 02:43.480
I guess if I get married,

02:43.800 --> 02:46.060
it'll take another seven or eight years.

02:47.280 --> 02:48.120
Eat your noodles.

02:48.120 --> 02:49.450
They're getting soggy.

03:38.520 --> 03:39.160
Grandma.

03:40.440 --> 03:41.400
I'm sorry.

03:43.040 --> 03:45.360
I couldn't come to see you one last time.

03:46.400 --> 03:48.920
I went to a competition to win prize money.

03:50.440 --> 03:52.160
I thought when I had the money,

03:53.520 --> 03:55.440
I could pay for your surgery.

04:00.320 --> 04:01.400
You go ahead.

04:02.240 --> 04:04.370
I want to stay with Grandma for a while.

04:07.520 --> 04:08.840
I'll wait for you outside.

04:08.840 --> 04:09.720
No need.

04:10.720 --> 04:11.780
You should go back.

04:14.160 --> 04:15.320
Yuanbao.

04:16.120 --> 04:17.320
Right now,

04:21.440 --> 04:23.100
I don't really want to see you.

04:32.040 --> 04:32.840
I understand.

04:34.440 --> 04:35.280
I know.

04:38.560 --> 04:40.960
Then stay safe,

04:41.920 --> 04:42.960
and go home early.

05:32.800 --> 05:34.480
I didn't dare to be too far from her,

05:34.480 --> 05:37.320
yet I didn't dare to go up and greet her.

05:38.400 --> 05:41.760
I was afraid seeing me would bring back sad memories.

05:42.920 --> 05:44.050
And even more afraid

05:44.600 --> 05:47.130
that she hated me from the bottom of her heart.

05:48.200 --> 05:50.320
I knew he wasn't far away.

05:50.880 --> 05:53.000
I didn't know how to face him now.

05:54.120 --> 05:57.580
I was afraid I wouldn't control my emotions and would hurt him.

05:57.920 --> 05:59.600
Although we were close,

05:59.720 --> 06:01.200
it felt like there was

06:01.320 --> 06:03.180
an uncrossable chasm between us.

06:03.640 --> 06:05.600
Though invisible and intangible,

06:06.080 --> 06:07.960
I knew the barrier was there.

06:08.600 --> 06:10.080
Our friendship of over ten years

06:10.080 --> 06:12.800
was now like a rainbow bubble in the sun.

06:13.880 --> 06:15.360
Still beautiful,

06:16.040 --> 06:18.840
but so fragile it could burst at any moment.

06:23.040 --> 06:26.160
Champion. Champion. Champion.

06:26.280 --> 06:27.600
The champion is back.

06:28.400 --> 06:30.040
Welcome, champion. Welcome, champion.

06:30.040 --> 06:31.440
Welcome, champion.

06:33.680 --> 06:35.159
Welcome, champion.

06:35.240 --> 06:36.400
Welcome, champion.

06:37.080 --> 06:38.280
Welcome, champion.

06:54.320 --> 06:55.850
Hello, Mr. Xu and Mr. Zhong.

06:56.600 --> 06:58.130
Come, who wants this candy?

06:58.280 --> 06:59.800
I do, I do, I do.

07:02.680 --> 07:04.680
Is Mr. Tian married with children?

07:04.760 --> 07:06.620
Those are the orphans he adopted.

07:07.320 --> 07:09.250
Mr. Tian pays for their education.

07:09.720 --> 07:11.800
Mr. Tian is such a role model.

07:12.280 --> 07:14.160
Even though he's poor as a church mouse,

07:14.160 --> 07:15.160
look at his shoes.

07:15.640 --> 07:17.080
And he's an older bachelor.

07:17.080 --> 07:18.680
But when it comes to charity,

07:18.880 --> 07:20.440
he doesn't hold back at all.

07:20.920 --> 07:22.960
How come I didn't hear about it before?

07:22.960 --> 07:24.360
Mr. Tian is very low-key.

07:25.000 --> 07:26.930
He didn't tell anyone else either.

07:27.880 --> 07:30.960
His children only come back to visit him once a year.

07:36.960 --> 07:38.840
Good, here's another reward for you.

07:38.840 --> 07:40.170
Come on, it's your turn.

07:48.960 --> 07:50.020
There is something

07:50.400 --> 07:52.360
I haven't had the chance to thank you for.

07:52.360 --> 07:53.080
What is it?

07:53.760 --> 07:56.020
When my grandmother was in the hospital,

07:56.120 --> 07:57.920
you helped me so much.

07:58.360 --> 08:00.800
I really don't know how to thank you.

08:01.160 --> 08:02.090
You're welcome.

08:02.400 --> 08:04.480
Isn't this what I'm supposed to do?

08:05.760 --> 08:08.840
Nothing in this world is a given.

08:11.400 --> 08:12.200
I mean,

08:12.760 --> 08:14.600
whatever someone does for another in this world

08:14.600 --> 08:16.040
shouldn't be taken for granted.

08:16.040 --> 08:19.080
I have taken your kindness to heart.

08:19.560 --> 08:22.360
I will slowly pay you back in the future.

08:23.800 --> 08:25.660
I didn't expect you to pay me back.

08:25.840 --> 08:28.760
No, I don't want to owe anyone anything.

08:28.960 --> 08:30.520
If you don't let me pay you back,

08:30.520 --> 08:32.400
I'll feel really bad.

08:34.120 --> 08:35.840
I really don't know what to do with you.

08:35.840 --> 08:37.700
So how are you going to pay me back?

08:39.760 --> 08:40.720
How about...

08:46.240 --> 08:48.240
How about you buy me a cup of milk tea?

08:49.400 --> 08:51.320
Just one cup of milk tea?

08:51.360 --> 08:53.160
Two cups wouldn't be bad either.

08:53.800 --> 08:54.460
Three cups.

08:54.800 --> 08:55.520
It's a deal.

08:56.200 --> 08:57.440
It's a deal.

09:00.080 --> 09:00.720
Let's go.

10:29.400 --> 10:30.930
Remember to eat breakfast.

11:19.280 --> 11:20.400
Ms. Tian, what's wrong?

11:20.400 --> 11:22.040
My bike chain fell off.

11:47.640 --> 11:49.880
Mr. Xu, you're amazing.

11:50.120 --> 11:51.200
How can I thank you?

11:52.280 --> 11:53.560
No need to thank me.

11:54.040 --> 11:55.570
You're pretty amazing too.

11:57.000 --> 11:57.680
Thanks.

11:59.240 --> 12:00.920
If your chain falls off again,

12:01.280 --> 12:04.080
you'll have to date me.

12:04.120 --> 12:04.840
Okay.

12:09.440 --> 12:10.200
Date you?

12:10.560 --> 12:11.640
M-Mr. Xu.

12:26.040 --> 12:27.300
You're looking for me?

12:28.320 --> 12:31.120
I noticed you haven't come over for dinner lately.

12:31.200 --> 12:32.800
I'm quite worried about you.

12:32.920 --> 12:34.640
Are you doing okay?

12:36.040 --> 12:36.840
I'm fine.

12:38.440 --> 12:39.520
Anything else?

12:41.440 --> 12:42.520
Well...

12:44.080 --> 12:46.200
I... I see you've been

12:46.640 --> 12:49.320
getting close to Meng Jingu lately.

12:49.760 --> 12:50.600
Are you two...

12:51.240 --> 12:52.720
We agreed

12:52.760 --> 12:55.240
to apply for universities in Beijing together.

12:55.240 --> 12:57.800
So he is continuing to tutor me.

12:59.440 --> 13:00.120
No.

13:01.120 --> 13:04.160
Didn't we agree to go to Beijing together?

13:06.240 --> 13:08.720
Did we? Did I say that?

13:10.360 --> 13:11.890
I probably don't remember.

13:12.480 --> 13:14.680
I think it's better for you to go abroad.

13:14.720 --> 13:16.000
I'm not going abroad.

13:16.320 --> 13:18.250
I've discussed it with my parents.

13:18.560 --> 13:19.560
I'm not leaving.

13:22.560 --> 13:23.490
All these years,

13:24.240 --> 13:26.570
I've always treated you as my own brother.

13:30.080 --> 13:32.600
I did before, and I still do now.

13:37.600 --> 13:38.520
I can't leave.

13:39.560 --> 13:40.680
We are family.

13:41.000 --> 13:42.600
We agreed to stick together.

13:43.000 --> 13:45.400
I promised Grandma I'd take care of you for the rest of my life.

13:45.400 --> 13:46.440
I can't leave.

13:48.520 --> 13:50.580
What nonsense are you talking about?

13:51.880 --> 13:54.720
Even biological brothers don't take care of each other for a whole lifetime.

13:54.720 --> 13:55.560
Besides...

13:58.440 --> 14:01.040
Besides, we've never been family.

14:01.760 --> 14:02.440
Yuanbao.

14:08.280 --> 14:09.080
Yuanbao.

14:12.200 --> 14:13.120
So you are here.

14:13.560 --> 14:15.020
I've been looking for you.

14:15.680 --> 14:16.640
Why are you here?

14:17.000 --> 14:19.330
Didn't I tell you to wait in the classroom?

14:21.560 --> 14:23.520
Qingyun, you're here too.

14:25.320 --> 14:26.120
Well,

14:27.000 --> 14:30.000
I have something to do, so I won't bother you.

14:30.800 --> 14:31.920
I'll get going.

14:54.560 --> 14:55.280
Qingyun.

14:56.320 --> 14:57.920
I don't know what to say.

14:58.720 --> 14:59.980
At first, I thought...

15:00.680 --> 15:03.120
I thought you were going to take the college entrance examination with everyone.

15:03.120 --> 15:04.000
I didn't expect

15:04.800 --> 15:06.200
you'd leave so suddenly.

15:06.320 --> 15:08.120
But going abroad is a good thing.

15:08.200 --> 15:11.560
I wish you a bright future and academic success.

15:12.320 --> 15:13.720
When you return to China,

15:13.880 --> 15:15.340
come back and visit often.

15:16.120 --> 15:16.880
Mr. Tian,

15:18.400 --> 15:21.880
I've caused you a lot of trouble these past few years.

15:24.160 --> 15:24.960
I'm sorry.

15:34.520 --> 15:35.780
I'm already used to it.

15:36.040 --> 15:38.640
Isn't this a characteristic of your age group?

15:40.520 --> 15:41.440
But

15:42.280 --> 15:43.240
if you leave,

15:44.720 --> 15:46.320
what will happen to Yuanbao?

16:00.600 --> 16:02.640
I'm saying goodbye to everyone today.

16:02.640 --> 16:04.370
I'm really glad you could come.

16:05.360 --> 16:07.020
What are you looking at me for?

16:07.200 --> 16:08.330
Drink up, everyone.

16:08.720 --> 16:09.360
Drink up.

16:09.520 --> 16:10.400
Brother, stop drinking.

16:10.400 --> 16:11.320
You can't drink like this.

16:11.320 --> 16:12.160
Drink less.

16:14.720 --> 16:16.600
All right.

16:16.680 --> 16:18.440
Even though we are eighteen,

16:18.800 --> 16:20.530
we still have school tomorrow.

16:22.400 --> 16:23.040
I forgot.

16:24.120 --> 16:25.450
I dropped out of school.

16:25.920 --> 16:27.520
You still have to go to school.

16:27.520 --> 16:28.440
You don't need to drink.

16:28.440 --> 16:29.640
Don't drink alcohol.

16:29.640 --> 16:30.560
Here are some drinks.

16:30.560 --> 16:31.960
Tea and cola.

16:32.760 --> 16:33.760
Help yourselves.

16:38.480 --> 16:40.880
I'm really glad you could come to see me off.

16:41.520 --> 16:43.800
Zhang Dongbo, thank you.

16:44.320 --> 16:46.120
Shang Ningyu, thank you.

16:47.520 --> 16:49.400
Ruirui, thank you.

16:49.520 --> 16:51.680
Qiao Yan, thank you.

16:52.280 --> 16:54.520
Class Monitor Xing Yaqi, thank you.

16:56.680 --> 16:59.280
Wang Zhiyong, PE rep, thank you.

17:00.440 --> 17:02.520
Gao Jingyi, thank you.

17:06.440 --> 17:07.800
I envy you.

17:22.640 --> 17:24.500
Why are you all looking like that?

17:24.640 --> 17:26.160
I'm just going abroad.

17:26.440 --> 17:28.440
It's not like I'm never coming back.

17:28.560 --> 17:30.440
Don't look so sad, you hear me?

17:31.240 --> 17:32.520
Let's be happy today.

17:32.840 --> 17:34.970
So I can leave with peace of mind, okay?

17:35.600 --> 17:37.240
Come, let's drink.

17:37.800 --> 17:40.400
Why don't you sing a song? I'll pick one for you.

18:20.120 --> 18:21.480
Listen up.

18:22.560 --> 18:23.360
After I leave,

18:24.240 --> 18:26.440
take good care of Xiong Yuanbao for me.

18:27.720 --> 18:29.720
If I find out anyone is bullying her,

18:30.400 --> 18:32.060
I'll kill them when I get back.

19:07.320 --> 19:08.250
What did you say?

19:09.680 --> 19:11.480
Take good care of Yuanbao.

19:20.480 --> 19:21.200
Qingyun.

19:21.760 --> 19:22.520
Qingyun.

19:25.120 --> 19:26.880
Yuanbao, you're here.

19:35.520 --> 19:36.640
He drank a lot.

19:37.840 --> 19:39.600
He kept shouting your name,

19:39.880 --> 19:41.480
so they called you.

19:43.280 --> 19:43.840
Mutou.

19:44.680 --> 19:45.200
Mutou.

19:45.920 --> 19:47.480
He's already dead drunk.

19:48.920 --> 19:50.200
Let's take him home.

20:16.440 --> 20:17.480
Yuan...

20:18.240 --> 20:19.560
Yuanbao,

20:20.600 --> 20:22.160
is that you?

20:29.800 --> 20:30.600
Yuanbao.

20:31.800 --> 20:33.680
Yuanbao, I'm sorry.

20:34.920 --> 20:36.720
It's all my fault.

20:38.080 --> 20:39.920
It's all my fault.

20:41.760 --> 20:43.360
Don't blame me.

20:44.160 --> 20:46.320
I don't want to leave.

20:47.800 --> 20:49.360
I'm sorry.

20:52.880 --> 20:54.440
We'll be home in a while.

20:56.120 --> 20:57.380
Sleep a little longer.

21:00.880 --> 21:01.600
No.

21:02.880 --> 21:06.880
I'm afraid you won't be here when I wake up.

21:08.760 --> 21:11.840
Yuanbao, I regret it.

21:13.240 --> 21:14.200
I'm not leaving.

21:15.440 --> 21:17.500
I'm going to stay and take care of you.

21:19.400 --> 21:23.200
I will spend the rest of my life making it up to you.

21:24.360 --> 21:25.400
What I owe you,

21:25.880 --> 21:27.120
what I owe Grandma,

21:27.440 --> 21:29.360
what I owe your parents,

21:30.600 --> 21:32.400
I will make it up to you all.

21:33.160 --> 21:35.880
I beg you, don't let me go.

21:41.400 --> 21:42.600
Please.

21:45.080 --> 21:45.960
Don't cry.

21:47.200 --> 21:49.560
Your head will hurt if you keep crying.

21:52.840 --> 21:54.170
Come on, get some sleep.

22:31.160 --> 22:31.760
All right.

22:49.800 --> 22:50.640
Yuanbao!

22:52.120 --> 22:52.960
Yuanbao!

22:57.320 --> 22:58.920
She probably went to school.

23:04.880 --> 23:05.520
Let's go.

23:06.520 --> 23:07.780
Don't miss the flight.

23:52.440 --> 23:53.640
Driver, stop the car.

23:59.640 --> 24:02.200
Mom, Dad.

24:02.680 --> 24:03.800
Give me some time.

24:35.560 --> 24:36.200
Yuanbao!

24:36.320 --> 24:37.180
Xiong Yuanbao!

24:37.240 --> 24:38.240
Open the door!

24:38.760 --> 24:39.840
Open the door!

24:40.040 --> 24:41.100
I know you're home!

24:41.200 --> 24:42.680
You... Open the door!

24:43.160 --> 24:44.320
Open the door!

24:45.560 --> 24:46.840
Open the door!

24:48.560 --> 24:49.360
I can't...

24:49.440 --> 24:50.720
I can't leave.

24:51.160 --> 24:53.400
I can't leave you at home alone.

24:53.720 --> 24:54.640
Yuanbao!

24:54.760 --> 24:56.560
What will you do alone, Yuanbao?

24:57.400 --> 24:58.240
Yuanbao!

25:00.640 --> 25:02.280
I promised Grandma.

25:04.640 --> 25:07.100
I promised Grandma I'd take good care of you.

25:07.600 --> 25:09.600
Open the door!

25:11.480 --> 25:12.720
Xiong Yuanbao!

25:13.760 --> 25:17.280
I beg you. Open the door!

25:36.840 --> 25:38.760
Open the door!

25:57.080 --> 25:58.040
I get it.

26:00.320 --> 26:01.720
Only if we leave

26:04.040 --> 26:05.720
can you forget

26:06.600 --> 26:08.240
those painful memories.

26:09.320 --> 26:10.000
Okay.

26:10.760 --> 26:11.480
I'll leave.

26:13.200 --> 26:14.330
Are you going or not?

26:14.520 --> 26:16.000
Wait a moment, sir.

27:06.360 --> 27:08.090
How do you solve this question?

27:32.000 --> 27:34.080
You two were so close back then.

27:34.240 --> 27:36.770
I thought something was going on between you.

27:37.040 --> 27:38.240
Besides, the rumors outside

27:38.240 --> 27:39.500
are spreading wildly.

27:42.320 --> 27:44.050
That's exactly what a rumor is.

27:45.160 --> 27:46.320
Rumors are all fake.

27:46.560 --> 27:47.680
What do you mean?

27:51.960 --> 27:53.690
Are you really going to do that?

27:58.800 --> 28:00.440
I don't want to hold him back.

28:01.800 --> 28:03.860
I want him to let go of everything here

28:04.600 --> 28:07.560
and pursue the better life that should belong to him.

28:08.240 --> 28:10.880
Even brothers don't take care of each other for a lifetime.

28:10.880 --> 28:11.600
Besides.

28:14.680 --> 28:17.280
Besides, we were never a family.

28:25.080 --> 28:26.400
Yuanbao.

28:29.600 --> 28:33.920
Actually, I've always liked you.

28:48.520 --> 28:49.160
Yuanbao.

28:49.280 --> 28:50.140
Xiong Yuanbao.

28:50.200 --> 28:51.200
Open the door.

28:51.720 --> 28:52.800
Open the door.

28:53.000 --> 28:54.160
I know you're at home.

28:54.160 --> 28:55.640
Open the door.

28:56.120 --> 28:57.280
Open the door.

28:58.520 --> 28:59.600
Open the door.

29:01.520 --> 29:02.320
I can't

29:02.400 --> 29:03.680
leave.

29:04.120 --> 29:06.360
I can't leave you alone at home.

29:06.680 --> 29:07.440
Yuanbao.

29:43.000 --> 29:46.120
Today I heard a very unfamiliar word,

29:46.280 --> 29:47.440
autism.

29:47.560 --> 29:48.840
I don't know why.

29:48.920 --> 29:50.880
Ever since Uncle and Aunt passed away,

29:50.880 --> 29:53.400
Yuanbao refuses to speak to anyone anymore.

29:53.800 --> 29:54.640
These days,

29:54.680 --> 29:57.760
I tried many ways to coax Yuanbao into speaking,

29:58.200 --> 30:00.000
but she just won't open her mouth.

30:00.000 --> 30:01.120
What should I do?

30:01.280 --> 30:03.600
I need to find a way to coax her.

30:03.640 --> 30:05.400
Yuanbao, I don't know how.

30:05.440 --> 30:07.160
Can you teach me?

30:07.400 --> 30:09.120
Yuanbao, I really don't know how to do this.

30:09.120 --> 30:10.600
Please teach me.

30:11.640 --> 30:13.480
I finally succeeded.

30:13.560 --> 30:15.520
As long as I ask her to explain problems to me,

30:15.520 --> 30:16.960
she's willing to talk.

31:59.560 --> 32:00.160
Boss.

32:02.680 --> 32:03.520
Wait a moment.

32:10.960 --> 32:11.400
Here.

32:11.480 --> 32:12.120
Thank you.

32:49.120 --> 32:51.560
If you're not in the group photo,

32:51.880 --> 32:53.400
what's the point?
